{"tid":2350223,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"［月經］入嚟放底你最鐘意嘅劇同戲","createTime":"2021-01-02T06:53:11.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-02T17:13:10.000Z","uid":146934,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"f17b840af3782351d3df7890ac262874e92d7c44","tid":2350223,"uid":146934,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-02T06:53:11.000Z","msg":"又sem break要毒喺屋企 <br />\n碌Netflix碌極都冇野好睇/睇咗<br />\n求推薦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我講先<br />\n劇：Inside no.9 九號祕事<br />\n呢套野係玩twist 每集唔同故事<br />\n有親情 恐怖 懸疑<br />\n睇第一集衣櫃已經睇到我呆撚咗<br />\n但身邊好少人講<br />\n我心目中神劇（沒有之一）<br />\n<br />\n戲：500 days of summer<br />\n套野唔算神但我好鐘意<br />\n其實feel到summer一直都好愛男主角<br />\n某程度係Tom唔識珍惜<br />\n成套野好平淡咁描述一段關係<br />\n但好真實<br />\n次次睇完都想喊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9a5dc90281dfa9fded70010596f6349d878ac694","tid":2350223,"uid":18912,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-02T07:03:40.000Z","msg":"When Harry Met Sally"},{"pid":"a8da11bf28bacdecbad0feecb3abcf36b00511b8","tid":2350223,"uid":103218,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-02T07:05:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://pic.pimg.tw/novapig/96542b32f278885e1ebfa9c09f7bcdbc.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpic.pimg.tw%2Fnovapig%2F96542b32f278885e1ebfa9c09f7bcdbc.png&h=98b9bf50&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"53377ef37a57dc85abb401c343e73e2706f3609d","tid":2350223,"uid":24227,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-02T16:00:13.000Z","msg":"Secret life of Walter Mitty <br />\nAbout Time<br />\nCoco"},{"pid":"d321bfc78bd93f52e1670a32e9fee49675082a57","tid":2350223,"uid":135316,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-02T16:01:53.000Z","msg":"戲：<br />\nAbout Time<br />\nEternal sunshine of the spotless mind<br />\nLove Rosie 劇情少老套 但音樂不錯"},{"pid":"267510bd5afbbaf5305011ee9107d3153ae29a4e","tid":2350223,"uid":27210,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-02T16:03:51.000Z","msg":"好多外國劇都好好睇<br />\n但我自己最鍾意係本土既天與地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c82ef673366dc382f1eea742cc3780eef41c9a5d","tid":2350223,"uid":382419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-02T16:55:07.000Z","msg":"一公升眼淚"},{"pid":"2afe0b4ff51660cca8d64a9cd536ee710209ccbd","tid":2350223,"uid":146934,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d321bfc78bd93f52e1670a32e9fee49675082a57","tid":2350223,"uid":135316,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-02T16:01:53.000Z","msg":"戲：<br />\nAbout Time<br />\nEternal sunshine of the spotless mind<br />\nLove Rosie 劇情少老套 但音樂不錯"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-02T17:13:10.000Z","msg":"最近有睇埋I am thinking of ending something<br />\n無痛失戀個導演<br />\n評價好兩極但我覺得都好正"}]}